  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dc5\u0dd4 \u0d9c\u0d9f \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db4\u0dc3 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0d85\u0dba\u0da7 \u0daf\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A notice to those on both sides of the Black River",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Irrigation Department has issued a flood warning in relation to the Kalu Ganga basin, valid until 03.00 pm tomorrow (01).",
        "The announcement further states that in the next 24 hours, a significant level of flooding may occur in the low-lying areas of Pelmadulla, Nivithigala, Ratnapura, Kuruvita, Ayagama and Alapatha Divisional Secretariat Divisions of Ratnapura District.",
        "Accordingly, the Irrigation Department further requests the people in those areas and those traveling through those areas to be very careful in this regard."
      ],
